<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DCC Podcasts</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bundle.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
      <a href="/">City Council Podcasts</a>
    </header>

    <main>
      <ul class="podcast-list">
        {%- for meeting in podcastData -%}
          <li class="listed-podcast">
            <a class="podcast-link" href="/meeting/{{ meeting.activity_id }}">{{ meeting.title }}</a>
            <p class="podcast-details">{{ meeting.isoDate | podcastDate }} | {{ meeting.content | podcastLocation }}</p>
          </li>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </ul>
      <section class="about">
        <p>This project makes Dublin City Council meetings available as podcasts, making it easier to subscribe and follow the council's activity.</p>
        <p>Available on <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/dublin-city-council-meetings/id1736170078">Apple Podcasts</a>, <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/4ihZPwAr3rXqASsb4E0flK?si=2f1dfbb2e5004bf0">Spotify</a>, or <a href="https://plinkhq.com/i/1736170078">wherever you get your podcasts.</a></p>
        <p>A <a href="https://fallowmedia.com">Fallow Media</a> project. RSS Feed available <a href="/feed.xml">here.</a> Source available <a href="https://github.com/Fallow-Media/dcc-podcasts">here.</a></p>
      </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>